  "page": "Rhaena Targaryen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Rhaena Targaryen</b> is the name of several members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a>, also known as <i>Queen in the West</i> and <i>Queen in the East</i>, eldest daughter and child of King Aenys I Targaryen, one of King Maegor I Targaryen's <i>Black Brides</i>, elder sister to King Jaehaerys I and Queen Alysanne Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Daemon)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Daemon)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a>, also known as <i>Rhaena of Pentos</i>, younger daughter of Prince Daemon Targaryen and Lady Laena Velaryon</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aegon_III)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aegon III)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a>, second daughter of King Aegon III Targaryen and Queen Daenaera Velaryon</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403162100\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.005 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:15891-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403162100 and revision id 323564\n -->\n",
